Configuring inn, either in sending or receiving mode, requires
the installation of:
	- the configuration files
	- news.daily
	- syslog

In addition, in receiving mode, the nsbp spool directory must be writeable
by the news user. There are two options:

	- On options is to make the spool diectory
	
		root:news  0775

	- the other is
		
		news:news  0755



	

